message.text:
Our short online course will provide you with a Level 3 Certificate in Principles of Management

This course will be delivered online, over 5 days and cover the main areas of management, including:

Responsibilities as a Manager
Objective Setting and Communicating to Support Teams 
Managing Self Development


These courses are available to unemployed residents of the West Midlands and are fully funded by the West Midlands Combined Authority.
